page.title: 19OKEHAMPTON BIRD LIST PAGE 4
page.content:
1= Very common, 2= Common, 3= Frequent 4= Uncommon, 5= Very rare.
Pied Flycatcher 2/3, Long-Tailed Tit 2, Marsh Tit 2, Willow Tit 3, Coal Tit 2, Blue Tit 1, Great Tit 1, Nuthatch 2, Treecreeper 2/3, Great Grey Shrike 4, Jay 1, Magpie 1, Jackdaw 1, Rook 1, Carrion Crow 1, Raven 1, Starling 1, House Sparrow 1, Tree Sparrow 4, Chaffinch 1, Brambling 3, Serin 5, Greenfinch 1, Goldfinch 2, Siskin 2/3, Linnet 2, Redpoll 3/4, Bullfinch 2/3, Snow Bunting 5, Yellowhammer 2, Reed Bunting 2.
A total of 115 different types of birds.
MARK GOLLEY. OKEHAMPTON, MARCH 1985
